# JavaScript for Modern Web Development (Alok Ranjan, Abhilasha Sinha etc.) (z - library.sk, 1lib.sk, z-lib.sk) — Passos Operacionais

Skill baseada no livro "JavaScript for Modern Web Development (Alok Ranjan, Abhilasha Sinha etc.) (z - library.sk, 1lib.sk, z-lib.sk)" (EN). Contem passos praticos e sequencias operacionais.

